name: THE ASTRAL PLANE
description:
Digital stereoscopic collage sourced from a collection of plane spotting editions called "Aircraft of the fighting powers", from 1944. Priced at 3d(pence) each at the time.

This image contains stereoscopic elements and comes with 2 pairs of red and blue 3D glasses.

"Giclee" print using the very best in photo imaging equipment – the Epson 9900 with its 11 colour Ultrachrome ink technology and the finest in archival Art Paper - Hahnemuhle Photorag 308gsm (Smooth)
